68
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:38,350
Kaisar bertitah meminta Selir Shu
ke Istana Jincheng untuk menemani.

69
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,070
Sekian.

70
00:07:42,350 --> 00:07:43,000
Selir Shu.

71
