Selir Shu.

202
00:18:28,719 --> 00:18:29,439
Haishi.

203
00:18:29,599 --> 00:18:30,040
Kau ini…

204
00:18:30,199 --> 00:18:31,479
Hati nuranimu sudah rusak.

205
00:18:42,319 --> 00:18:43,079
Wangi sekali.

206
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,199
Guru.

207
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,719
Aku bilang ini harum sekali.

208
00:18:54,439 --> 00:18:54,839
Ini…

209
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,040
Hebat kau.

210
00:18:56,319 --> 00:18:57,359
Manfaatkan barangku.

211
00:18:57,599 --> 00:18:58,040
Guru.

212
00:18:58,199 --> 00:18:59,119
Ini punyaku.

213
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:01,880
Kembalikan padanya.

214
00:19:08,280 --> 00:19:08,839
Guru.

215
00:19:08,959 --> 00:19:10,640
Jika tak ada hal lain,
saya pamit dulu.

216
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:17,400
Ada perlu mencarimu.

217
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,239
Ada apa Guru mencariku?

218
00:19:20,599 --> 00:19:21,800
Beberapa hari ini istirahat,…

219
00:19:22,079 --> 00:19:24,560
…kebetulan mau pergi
ke pantai di Desa Linjie.

220
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:27,640
Jika kau ingin pulang,
bisa berangkat bersama Guru.

